OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLow cloud across the east in
OL,6,Fthe morning will burn back to the east
OL,7,Fcoast, lingering in a few places into
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Otherwise dry and
OL,9,Fsunny. Very warm or hot in the
OL,10,Fsouthwest, but cooler in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with some late sunshine
OL,13,Fthis evening away from the east coast.
OL,14,FThen dry overnight with low cloud
OL,15,Facross the east but staying clear
OL,16,Felsewhere.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FLow cloud in the east
OL,19,Fburning back to the coast, otherwise
OL,20,Fdry and sunny. Very warm or hot in the
OL,21,Fsouthwest, cooler in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
